### FHIR Bulk Export Operations ($export)
### Uses DurableTask framework for background processing
### Based on: https://hl7.org/fhir/async.html

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5027
@tenantId = 1

### 1. Start System-Level Export (all resource types)
# @name startSystemExport
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/$export
Accept: application/fhir+json
Prefer: respond-async

###

### 2. Start System-Level Export (specific resource types)
# @name startFilteredExport
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/$export?_type=Patient,Observation
Accept: application/fhir+json
Prefer: respond-async

###

### 3. Start Export with Since Parameter (incremental export)
# @name startIncrementalExport
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/$export?_type=Patient&_since=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z
Accept: application/fhir+json
Prefer: respond-async

###

### 4. Start Export with Type Filter (advanced filtering)
# @name startTypeFilterExport
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/$export?_type=Observation&_typeFilter=Observation?code=http://loinc.org|8867-4
Accept: application/fhir+json
Prefer: respond-async

###

### 5. Poll Export Job Status
# Replace {jobId} with the ID from Content-Location header
# @name pollExportStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/_export/{jobId}
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### 6. Cancel Export Job
# Replace {jobId} with the ID from Content-Location header
# @name cancelExport
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenant/{{tenantId}}/_export/{jobId}

###

### Expected Response Flow:
# 1. POST $export returns 202 Accepted with Content-Location header
# 2. Poll GET _export/{jobId} returns:
#    - 202 Accepted (still processing) with X-Progress header
#    - 200 OK (completed) with output file links in JSON body
# 3. Download output files from URLs in response

### Example Completed Response Body:
# {
#   "transactionTime": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z",
#   "request": "https://localhost:5027/tenant/1/$export?_type=Patient",
#   "requiresAccessToken": false,
#   "output": [
#     {
#       "type": "Patient",
#       "url": "https://localhost:5027/tenant/1/_export/files/job-123/Patient_001.ndjson"
#     }
#   ],
#   "error": []
# }
